它的名字叫道風山,是香港沙田的一座建築,是由一個基督教信義中的宣教士建立的。他把教會聚會的地方刻意以中國佛教寺院的形式去建立,希望基督教以中國化的形式去傳福音。

13
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:37,000
在1930年代規劃,目的是向剛剛說佛教、道教的教徒去傳福音,讓他們能夠在熟悉的宗教環境裏面接觸到宗教信仰。

14
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:56,000
So the name of the building is called Tao Feng Shan, a building in Hong Kong, it was designed in the 1930s by Norwegian Lutheran missionary who deliberately built a church meeting place in the style of a Chinese Buddhist temple, hoping to spread the gospel of Christianity in a Chinese way.

15
00:01:56,000 --> 00:02:04,000
The aim was to evangelize Buddhists and Taoists, allow them to encounter the Christian faith in a familiar religious space.

16
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:33,000
